{"tid":1740241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］政府諗緊咩 我地下一步","createTime":"2019-11-20T01:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T00:30:07.000Z","uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a2a84f2eb90b300ce9dee58bedf93a385476ce12","tid":1740241,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:18:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1) 點解政府今日要復課？</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">- 我認為佢地目的係要恢復星期三至五既「和你塞」，藉此以公眾秩序為由取消區議會選舉。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2)如果政府意在取消區議會選舉，我地就要問區選對運動重唔重要？</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">- 我認為重要。好簡單，寸土必爭，體制內外都要籌碼、力量。<br />\n<br />\n- 區議員一來可以為下年立法會候選人做椿腳，二來佔特首選委差唔多10%。冇錯，我地唔同意現行既立法會、特首選舉機制；但要推翻現行制度，制度內外都要有我地既力量、手足。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3) 如果大家認為區選對運動重要，咁下一步應該點行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">- 我地要做既，就係唔好俾藉口政府，由聽日起至下星期二(下星期一要點票)，要停火(汽油彈、裝修、縱火)、暫停「和你塞」。<br />\n<br />\n- 如果停火後，政府照樣取消區選，只會得罪更多人，包括藍絲。<br />\n<br />\n- 無論政府最終決定如何，我唔覺得停火5日有咩問題。停5日後再聚人會好困難？請相信手足、香港人。<br />\n<br />\n- 呢場係Water Revolution，希望大家可以繼續be water，能收能放。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果同意，請考慮出份停火聲明，再集中文宣攻勢。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"964b6caec4d0622a3a2c2cfec31b8d14a2672892","tid":1740241,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:21:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e28eb7e1d35549e63ea13b12550f24024e075b59","tid":1740241,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:26:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92e4493e54eb280acdf77b7ffc4380a838b0b516","tid":1740241,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:26:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d34f3622d0d277aa7e7520d79eace9ae4616d529","tid":1740241,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:27:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef2a829164114270142be52860bfb09c96310350","tid":1740241,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:27:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ca1fba760395f795538ca1583bc17511cef14a9","tid":1740241,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:27:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fbd5f3698a554cc2ba895067183e8f2f00cb633","tid":1740241,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:27:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"284962b18ae961c8073a4c55025a2f33fa200e78","tid":1740241,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:27:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d19897b7e061cba8b04a46e0bae4d9a70f981163","tid":1740241,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:28:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69efcaaf28429b5d50be5f488fa6a9a3d9772507","tid":1740241,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:28:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1b093d098b3d05b18f6937eaf519ac50e1bc2c","tid":1740241,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a5e5d7ec65633bbb45bf67cef8bd2aa1250bfa","tid":1740241,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e57ea2c73534244edbb34ca12b538202606558","tid":1740241,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:30:50.000Z","msg